<h2 class="title">News&nbsp;</h2><hr style="width: 100%; height: 2px;" /><h3>Tweenie Tots</h3><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; display: inline ! important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Books
are the focus and fun is the goal. Preschoolers are invited to join in
the stories, songs, rhymes and crafts. Each week will be a new theme
and a new opportunity to learn and laugh during this 45 minute program.
</span>Children
must be accompanied by an adult.&nbsp; The program is on Thursday
mornings 10:30 -11:15 a.m.
and the donation is $1/child/session.  <span style="font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;The new session starts on September 15, 2016.</span><hr style="width: 100%; height: 2px;" /><span style="font-weight: bold;"></span><div style="text-align: center;"><div style="text-align: left;"><h3>Friends of the West Perth Library Bus Trip<img style="float: right; width: 229px; height: 94px;" alt="Too darn hot" src="images/small_too_darn_hot2.png" hspace="2" vspace="2" /></h3>When: &nbsp; &nbsp; Friday, October 21<br />Where: &nbsp; &nbsp;Famous PEOPLE Players Theatre<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;in Toronto<br />Cost: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; $100/person - includes bus trip, hot<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;lunch and theatre ticket<br />Time: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Bus leaves Mitchell at 8:45 am and<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;arrives back in Mitchell around 6 pm<br /><br />For more information call Juanita at 519-348-4609 or the library at 519-348-9234.<hr style="width: 100%; height: 2px;" /><h3>Shake, Wiggle and Roll<img style="float: right; width: 170px; height: 170px;" alt="shake, wiggle and roll" src="images/shake,%20wiggle%20and%20roll.png" hspace="2" vspace="2" /></h3><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; display: inline ! important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">"Shake,
Wiggle and Roll" is a program for infants 4 - 12 months offered by the
West Perth Early Years Centre and taking place at the Library, Fridays
Sept. 9-30 10:15-11:00 am. It is a time for parents to engage with
their children for a time of music, movement and hands-on activities.
Please register with the Early Years Centre at 519-348-8618.</span><br /><hr style="width: 100%; height: 2px;" /><h3>Recreation &amp; Leisure Services Master Plan</h3><span style="color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: helvetica,arial,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 19.32px; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; display: inline ! important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span class="Apple-converted-space">The Recreation &amp; Leisure Services Master Plan can be read <a href="15-1800%20Master%20Plan_Public%20Draft_June%202016%202.pdf">here</a> and the Summary of Recommendations <a href="15-1800_Summary%20of%20Recommendations%20_June%202016_Draft.pdf">here</a>.
This study is to help shape the future of recreation &amp; leisure in
West Perth. &nbsp;A printed copy is available at the library for
reading.</span></span><hr style="width: 100%; height: 2px;" /><h3>Young Adult Book Club</h3>Come
join other young adults once a month to share the enjoyment of reading
books of all genres in a fun and casual atmosphere. Planned for those
young people in grades 8, 9 and 10. &nbsp;Meetings will occur on designated Mondays. Please contact the library
for the coordinator's name.&nbsp;<hr style="width: 100%; height: 2px;" /><h3>Gallery Space</h3>
The library has a display space on Level 3.
&nbsp;Now exhibiting are paintings from Perth County resident Jean Stevenson.<span style="font-weight: bold;"></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"></span></div><hr style="width: 100%; height: 2px;" /></div><span style="font-style: italic;"></span>
<div class="story"><h3><span style="font-weight: bold;"></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"></span>Do you know about &nbsp;.... our online information?
Featuring:</h3><img style="width: 150px; height: 75px; float: left;" alt="Novelist" src="images/novelist.gif" hspace="10" /><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline ! important; float: none;"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Novelist</span><br />This
database allows readers to search for their favourite authors or
titles, and find others of similar interest. &nbsp;Users can browse
theme-oriented book lists at every reading level through Explore
Fiction, and look for outstanding titles in Best Fiction.<br /><br /></span><a href="http://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?authtype=ip,cpid&amp;custid=ns022607&amp;profile=novelist" style="color: rgb(58, 105, 186); font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Use in Library or online from outside of Library</a><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline ! important; float: none;"></span><br /><br /><br />
Visit the <a href="databases.htm">Online Databases
&amp; Newspapers</a> page to see all available databases.
